      <div class="model-card"><h3>ThinQ AI + firmware</h3><p>LG ThinQ app manages both compartments in one interface. Firmware updates push shared across washer + dryer concurrently. Pairing + reset procedures mirror standalone LG appliances but apply to the shared system.</p></div>
